_______________________________________________________________________________
"Hypnotize"        
 
        This allows the psionicist to hypnotize a target into
        believing that he sees something that is not actually there.
        The target will see a message to the effect of, 'You
        think you see <message>'
 
SP Cost:  5		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  1
 
Command: hypnotize <target> <message>
